  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/8c8dabb6cb6385de2d82154efe31da16.poster.avif?t=1762854781\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/8c8dabb6cb6385de2d82154efe31da16.webm?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/8c8dabb6cb6385de2d82154efe31da16.mp4?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Brief story</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They thought the era of ash and dust had ended. Yet shadows have stirred again, and prophecy unfolds. Born under the moonlight, the white-haired girl Elia alone can stand against the fallen star. Awakened atop the tower, she takes up the flame to stop the nightmare overtaking the world. Now, darkness threatens once more. You hold the blade of destiny.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Overview</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slayer is a strategic action game built around a finely tuned combat system and dark narrative. Survival demands more than quick reflexes—you must consider movement direction, positioning, attack angles, parrying, dodging timing, and map structure.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>New Mode Added!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try out the newly added Boss Challenge Mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face a series of powerful bosses and shape your own combat style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/f3c5163349976c6072de31a3f2f86577.poster.avif?t=1762854781\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/f3c5163349976c6072de31a3f2f86577.webm?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/f3c5163349976c6072de31a3f2f86577.mp4?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/e72961f0f5cf8c4d8d3d4a25eb9a603e.poster.avif?t=1762854781\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/e72961f0f5cf8c4d8d3d4a25eb9a603e.webm?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/e72961f0f5cf8c4d8d3d4a25eb9a603e.mp4?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Three Modes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Action Mode</strong>: Full directional attacks and combo-driven, exhilarating gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Master Mode</strong>: Front-facing attacks only. Precise positioning and strategy are essential.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Hardcore Mode</strong>: Limited lives, permadeath upon depletion. For extreme survivalists.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/1b1d7aacb390ed9687f22f41639d144c.poster.avif?t=1762854781\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/1b1d7aacb390ed9687f22f41639d144c.webm?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/1b1d7aacb390ed9687f22f41639d144c.mp4?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Combat & Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Strategic Souls-like combat</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Puzzle-like stage design</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Bosses with unique patterns and mechanics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Short, intense combat experiences</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/b01d28349b26cefd9dbe891a6f9babd4.poster.avif?t=1762854781\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/b01d28349b26cefd9dbe891a6f9babd4.webm?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/b01d28349b26cefd9dbe891a6f9babd4.mp4?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Coming Soon: Fallen Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arriving October 2024—an expansion-like mode with new maps, enemies, bosses, and a darker, highly strategic atmosphere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/ca8a3c43be01ff69539d1f246a85c9fe.poster.avif?t=1762854781\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/ca8a3c43be01ff69539d1f246a85c9fe.webm?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/ca8a3c43be01ff69539d1f246a85c9fe.mp4?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/bb5c957b4618ea9b34a150ee578be6a0.avif?t=1762854781\" width=800 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discord </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/8c8dabb6cb6385de2d82154efe31da16.poster.avif?t=1762854781\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/8c8dabb6cb6385de2d82154efe31da16.webm?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/8c8dabb6cb6385de2d82154efe31da16.mp4?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Brief story</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They thought the era of ash and dust had ended. Yet shadows have stirred again, and prophecy unfolds. Born under the moonlight, the white-haired girl Elia alone can stand against the fallen star. Awakened atop the tower, she takes up the flame to stop the nightmare overtaking the world. Now, darkness threatens once more. You hold the blade of destiny.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Overview</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slayer is a strategic action game built around a finely tuned combat system and dark narrative. Survival demands more than quick reflexes—you must consider movement direction, positioning, attack angles, parrying, dodging timing, and map structure.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>New Mode Added!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try out the newly added Boss Challenge Mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face a series of powerful bosses and shape your own combat style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/f3c5163349976c6072de31a3f2f86577.poster.avif?t=1762854781\" width=720 height=404 ><sou