tem_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/1b1d7aacb390ed9687f22f41639d144c.mp4?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Combat & Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Strategic Souls-like combat</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Puzzle-like stage design</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Bosses with unique patterns and mechanics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Short, intense combat experiences</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/b01d28349b26cefd9dbe891a6f9babd4.poster.avif?t=1762854781\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/b01d28349b26cefd9dbe891a6f9babd4.webm?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/b01d28349b26cefd9dbe891a6f9babd4.mp4?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Coming Soon: Fallen Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arriving October 2024—an expansion-like mode with new maps, enemies, bosses, and a darker, highly strategic atmosphere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/ca8a3c43be01ff69539d1f246a85c9fe.poster.avif?t=1762854781\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/ca8a3c43be01ff69539d1f246a85c9fe.webm?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/ca8a3c43be01ff69539d1f246a85c9fe.mp4?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/mp4\